dct_description_sm: Title supplied by cataloger. Wall maps. Each map is cloth backed and mounted on wooden rods in a scroll. Library has: 11. Hai Staurophoriai apo to 1096-1192; 12. Hē Hell. Anatolē meta tēn 4ēn Staurophorian; 13. Hē Eurōpē meta tēn enkatastasin tōn Tourkōn 1453-1566; 15. Hellada kata tēn periodo tēs Epanastasēs 1821.
